Paul Gutrecht https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Gutrecht 0 Paul Gutrecht (born September 5, 1967) is an American actor, writer, director, producer, and therapist. He played Mark Wilson in the first entry of the Saw film series. He has also had guest appearances in television series.
